item.title: Mar 2015 meetup
item.description:
Another month, another meetup! This time it'll be on the 26th of March at the ThoughtWorks' office.

Venue: 87B Amoy Street #03/04, Singapore 069906, Singapore

If you want to attend then please sign up on our meetup page, as there is limited space please only mark yourself as attending …
